{"tid":2189073,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白宮大規模清查政府所有涉中國資金 疑為進一步抗中行動鋪路","createTime":"2020-09-04T15:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T16:18:21.000Z","uid":28765,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"278739d190403e94729ff141eb1f1d78d7249cec","tid":2189073,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T15:36:39.000Z","msg":"美國與中國緊張關係持續惡化之際，白宮要求聯邦政府各部門，21日前提交任何有關支持或直接、間接對抗中國影響力和商業行為的資金細節。美國政府此舉可能是在為對中國採取更多行動鋪路。<br />\n<br />\n「路透」4日獨家報導，白宮行政管理暨預算辦公室（OMB）日期註為8月27日的文件「與中國的戰略競爭剖析」，指示各單位提交「聯邦資金用於支援或支持，或者直接、間接對抗中國不公平競爭、惡意活動和在全球影響力的細節資料」；文件中只說這些資料將用於「提供決策者」了解美國政府涉及中國的開支，並未進一步說明如何使用。<br />\n<br />\n這份備忘錄特別指出，列出用於「對抗不符合美國利益的中國惡意影響力或行為」之政府資金，如對抗「一帶一路倡議」、提供軍方活動、軍備和基礎設施資金，以及對抗中國在第五代行動通訊技術（5G）、無線通訊、半導體、人工智慧、機器學習、量子運算、網路安全、自動化和電動車、生物科技和太空等科技能力，以及衛生部、國家衛生研究院涉及中國的計畫資金；<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n白宮在指示中說，要求檢視「對中國國內生產總值（GDP）或政府、軍事單位技術實力、國營商業或工業實體、職能直接受中國政府領導階層指揮之實體」有整體貢獻之開支。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3282164\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3282164&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs42XOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=0613533f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3282164&h=48adcdfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3282164</a>"},{"pid":"d6fcb1f2b32e2ee2a888ec3d9512897439e8dcd8","tid":2189073,"uid":273218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T15:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國加油"},{"pid":"2ffb8d236812bcef17e346c16b9dce08077b35fa","tid":2189073,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T15:40:16.000Z","msg":"拜登一上任白宮就會冇左4騎士,唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c4d1e77936fb5b41e4eb82476f5fa564f89e6b","tid":2189073,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T15:51:23.000Z","msg":"聯署支持封殺微信同TikTok<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fwe-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs42XOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=0d924078\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok</a>"},{"pid":"404736b5b347f4707304e36cd042adb40ea57e6c","tid":2189073,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T15:53:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2123928caa5929de9453f12e8b08169a2275f1e3","tid":2189073,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T15:56:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac64d13f122a0364258e96280fc74949ec151ef8","tid":2189073,"uid":374259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T16:18:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}